<plot>After suffering from a severe personal loss, Kray (Phil MacFadden) decides to escape it all and head to Vegas for a week. But, when Kray picks up a Native American hitchhiker (Zan Calabretta), everything is turned upside down and Kray begins to question the meaning and purpose of his existence. This is a story with a very strong spiritual message that shows that life and its mysteries are all about perspective.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?429851</url></doc>
